name: Front Parking Lights
description:
S2k LEDs are not only brighter than the stock bulbs, they are much more attractive. Giving your s2k a more modern and sophisticated look.

S2k LEDs use less power consumption than standard bulbs and last 10x longer than incandescent bulbs. No longer will you have a dead battery after leaving your lights on.
